This paper deals with an online algorithm problem in a normed space, which involves maintaining a competitive ratio against an optimal offline solution. This problem is related to computational complexity (cs.CC), as well as data structures (cs.DS) and game theory (cs.GT). The paper also involves optimization techniques (cs.MG) and numerical analysis (cs.NA) in its approach.
